data.description: This one-of-a-kind custom home w/ grand foyer, spacious living area, & stunning white oak flooring, it exudes elegance. The chef's kitchen is a standout w/ top-of-the-line appliances, 2 dishwashers, captivating waterfall window, & Turkish marble floors. Panoramic mountain & city views can be enjoyed from almost every room. With 2 primary suites, walk-in closets, ensuite baths, 2 newer high-efficiency heat pumps, 2 laundry areas, this home has it all! 2 basements are perfect for storage. GREAT location just minutes to Good Sam Hospital, 512 & 167. The majestic top of Puyallup views are unmatched! Needs a new roof. Great opportunity to get this home at a discount - bring your tools & come put your finishing touches on this unique home!
